@EndNode

@Node "Buttons"
@Next "To do"
@Prev "Getting started"
@Toc "Main"

KEYS
¯¯¯¯
 - Instant play with F1-F10 and the numeric 1-4 keys.
   When pressing a key, the sample data is allready loaded into memory.
   The only time delay it takes to play a sample is for the HD to seek
   to the right position in the file.

 - Pressing left or right arrow will load previous or next preset

 - Pressing RETURN will play the next sample in that preset.

 - Pressing SPACE will play the laste sample played.

 - While playing, pressing ESC stops playing the sample.

@EndNode

